{"tid":245250,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後中文水平奇差，叫佢較低 d部冷氣竟然較大個溫度！","createTime":"2017-05-16T05:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T05:35:47.000Z","uid":19334,"like":6,"dislike":103,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c9569a4e5f006d86a452d439205774b429efd6","tid":245250,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"話說呢排天氣又濕又熱，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁正常人返工都要嘆冷氣架啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁番工行到身水身汗，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n番到Office 開到部冷氣勁低亦都不無道理！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁開到十二點幾，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得凍凍地，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我咪同隻90後講「幫我較低 d部冷氣！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知條友唔知係咪聽力有問題，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由今朝既18度較到落15度，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原全唔識用腦！睇下眉頭眼額就知我凍啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要連中文都聽唔明，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下次真係要成句完整句子講哂出黎，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一簡短小小就Get錯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f520e7128d4a6f0a598539c058a25a4563878979","tid":245250,"uid":24217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:00:17.000Z","msg":"？？？"},{"pid":"2a1fb597ece04459a4658c6725f7169ab22571a5","tid":245250,"uid":49782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"較細<br />\n較大"},{"pid":"53d7aaf2ccd021196b049970c3ab43371d103956","tid"